.TH "ep_from_windex" 9 "ep_from_windex" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ep_from_windex \- convert control wIndex value to endpoint
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct dwc2_hsotg_ep *" ep_from_windex
.BI "(struct dwc2_hsotg *hsotg "  ","
.BI "u32 windex "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hsotg" 12
The driver state.
.IP "windex" 12
The control request wIndex field (in host order).
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Convert the given wIndex into a pointer to an driver endpoint
structure, or return NULL if it is not a valid endpoint.
